quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  7,88,"Hooree…ìe mbatu townitii…ìe …ìen e yim…ìe Su'aybu men …ìen wi'i : "Ko maa men yaltinndine an Su'aybu -e ndee saare amen- e …ìen goongim…ìe ma, maa rutto…óon e diina amen kan". -Su'aybu jaabitii…ìe …ìe : "E men jokkay diina mon hay me…óen a√±iri ka tawde ko ka diina meere?!"."
  7,89,"Gom…óii haray men bakii fenannde e hoore Alla si men fi…ìii pi…ìe mon sirku e keeferaaku …ìaawo nde Alla hisini men e …óum. Haananaa men nde men ruttoo e diina mon meere kan si wanaa nde Alla Joomi muuyi. Joomi amen huu…ìitirii kala huunde Anndal, huunde suu…óaaki Mo. Ko e Alla woni ko men fawii fii ko √±ii…ìina men e laawol focciingol da…ónda men laawol Yiite. Joomi amen, √±aawir hakkunde e yim…ìe amen heefer…ìe …ìen goonga, wallito…óaa jom-goonga kan e hoore too√±u…óo on, ko An Joomi amen …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e √±aawoo…ìe …ìen."
  7,90,"Hooree…ìe mbatu yeddu…ìe …ìen e yim…ìe makko …ìen salii…ìe Tawhiidi …ìen wi'i no rentina e diina Su'aybu : "Pellet, si on naatii e diina Su'aybu kan -onon yim…ìe amen- on selii diina mon e diina maw…ìe mo'on, haray on wonii halkii…ìe"."
  7,91,"Dillaango tii…óungo nanngi …ìe, …ìe wa…ótini halkaa…ìe ka ko…óooli ma…ì…ìe, jiccii…ìe ugginii, maayu…ìe …ìutti e galle ma…ì…ìe."
  7,92,"∆Åen fennunoo…ìe Su'aybu, …ìe halkino …ìe denndaangal, …ìe wa…ótini a sikkay …ìe mee…óaa √±ii…ìude e ho…óo ma…ì…ìe. ∆Åen fennunoo…ìe Su'aybu, …ìe laatino kam…ìe woni hayru…ìe ; tawde …ìe hayruno wonikiiji ma…ì…ìe e piiji ma…ì…ìe, wonaa gom…óim…ìe …ìen wonunoo ko hayri wano …ìee heefer…ìe fenoo…ìe aa∆¥ornoo."
  7,93,"Annabaajo ma…ì…ìe on Su'aybu (yo o his) …óuurnii …ìe tuma nde …ìe halkinoo, o maakani …ìe : "Ko onon yim…ìe am, gom…óii le mi yottinii Nule Joomi am …óen e moo…óon, mi laabanii on reedu on ja…ìaali. E ko honno mi sunorta e yim…ìe yeddu…ìe Alla ha…ì…ìitii e …óum?!"."
  7,94,"Men nulaali e saare woo Annabaajo Alla, yim…ìe mayre …ìen fenni mo …ìe yeddi, si wanaa Men nanngitirii …ìe sa…óteende baasal e √±abbuuli jortagol nde …ìe yankinantoo Alla …ìe tertoo keeferaaku e townitaare. ∆äum non ko jertingol Quraysiyankoo…ìe …ìen e kala yeddu…óo fenni e mofte …óen."
  7,95,"Refti men wa…ótitiri nokku bone on mo∆¥∆¥ere e hoolaare, haa …ìe …óuu…ói e adadu, jawle ma…ì…ìe …ìeydii, …ìe wi'i : "Kala bone e mo∆¥∆¥ere ko he…ìi men, …óum ko woowaa…óum, he…ìiino maamiraa…ìe amen". ∆Åe anndaa non wonnde ko he…ìi …ìe kon e lepte ko fii no …ìe waajitora, ko he…ìi kon kadi e neema ko fii no …ìe …óoftora. Men nanngiri …ìe lepte …óen e juhal, hari kam…ìe …ìe so'aa anndude …ìe habbanooki …óum."